[{"Id": 1013640, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Sadiq (a) says: If any sorrowful person will pray this namaz, Allah will ward off his sorrow, so after praying the Maghrib Namaz and its Naafelah, recite 2 rakat namaz for the honoring of the Masjid then raise your hands and recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Sadiq (a) ne farmaya: Koi gham zadah shakhs is namaz ko anjaam dega, to Allah (swt) uske gham ko dur kar dega, to Maghrib aur uski naafela ke baad 2 rakat namaz padhe Tahiyyate Masjid ki niyyat se aur phir apne haatho’n ko buland karke is tarah padhe…", "UrduDescription": "نمازِ مغرب اور اس کی نافلہ کو ادا کرے، پھر کھڑے ہوکر ۲ رکعت نمازِ تحیت مسجد قربۃً الی اللہ کی نیت سے بجا لائے اس کے بعد اپنے ہاتھوں کو آسمان کی طرف بلند کرکے یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013641, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "You are Allah; there is no god save You. You are the Beginner of the process of creation and the Repeater of it. You are Allah; there is no god save You. You are the Creator of creatures and the Sustainer of them. You are Allah; there is no god save You. You are the Straightener and the Expander. You are Allah; there is no god save You. You are the Manager of all affairs and the Resurrector of those who are in graves. You are the Inheritor of the earth & whatever, whoever is on it.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Tu woh Allah hai keh jis ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi hai jo khalq ka aaghaaz karne aur usey lauta ne waala hai, Tu woh Allah hai keh jis ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi jo makhlooq ko paiyda karne aur rizq dene waala hai, Tu woh Allah hai Tere siwa koi ma’bood nahi, rokne waala aur ataa karne waala hai, Tu woh Allah hai keh jis ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi jo maamlaat ko chala ne waala aur qabro’n mein se zindah utha ne waala hai, Tu waaris hai zameen ka jo kuchh us par hai.", "Urdu": "تو وہ اللہ ہے کہ جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں ہے جو خلق کا آغاز کرنے اور اسے لوٹانے والا ہے تو وہ اللہ ہے کہ جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو مخلوق کو پیدا کرنے اور رزق دینے والا ہے تو وہ اللہ ہے تیرے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں تو روکنے والا اور عطا کرنے والا ہے تو وہ اللہ ہے کہ جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو معاملات کو چلانے والا اور قبروں میں سے زندہ اٹھانے والا ہے تو وارث ہے زمین کا اورجو کچھ اس پر ہے۔", "RArabic": "ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLA ANTA MUBDE-UL KHALQE WA MO-E’EDOHUM WA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTAL KHAALEQUL KHALQE WA RAAZEQOHUM WA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTAL QAABEZUL BAASETO WA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA MODABBERUL OMOORE WA BAA-E’SO MAN FIL QOBOORE ANTA WAARESUL ARZE WA MAN A’LAYHAA.", "ArabicText1": "اَنْتَ اللہُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ مُبْدِیُٔ الْخَلْقِ وَمُعِیْدُھُمْ۔ وَاَنْتَ اللہُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ الْخَالِقُ الْخَلْقِ وَرَازِقُهُمْ۔ وَاَنْتَ اللہُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ الْقَابِضُ الْبَاسِطُ۔ وَاَنْتَ اللہُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ مُدَبِّرُ الْاُمُوْرِ وَبَاعِثُ مَنْ فِیْ الْقُبُوْرِ اَنْتَ وَارِثُ الْاَرْضِ وَمَنْ عَلَیْھَا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013642, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I beseech You by Your Name: the concealed, the obscured, the ever-living, and the self-subsistent. You are Allah; there is no god save You. You are the Knower of secrets and what is yet more hidden. I beseech You by Your Name: a Name that You respond to him who beseeches You by it and the Name that You give him who asks You by it. And I beseech You in the name of the duty of Muhammad and his Household towards You and in the name of the duty that You have made incumbent upon Yourself towards them to send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and to grant me my requests at this very hour! At this very hour! O Hearer of prayers!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai sawaal karta hu Tujh se Tere mehfooz, poshida, zindah o paainda naam ke waaste se, Tu woh Allah hai keh jis ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi jo poshida aur makhfi cheezo’n ko jaanne waala hai. Sawaal karta hu Tujh se Tere us naam se keh jab Tujhe us se pukaara jaaye to jawaab deta hai, jab uske zariye maanga jaaye to ataa karta hai. Sawaal karta hu Tujh se ba-waasta Tere haq ke jo Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unke Ahlebait (a.s) par hai aur ba-waasta unke haq ke jo Tu ne apni zaat par laazim kiya hai yeh keh Tu rehmat naazil farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par, neez yeh keh Tu meri haajat puri farma abhi, isi waqt, isi ghadi ay dua ke soonne waale.", "Urdu": "میں سوال کرتا ہوں تجھ سے تیرے محفوظ پوشیدہ زندہ وپائندہ نام کے واسطے سے تو وہ اللہ ہے کہ جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو پوشیدہ اور مخفی چیزوں کو جاننے والا ہے سوال کرتا ہوں تجھ سے تیرے اس نام سے کہ جب تجھے اس سے پکارا جائے تو جواب دیتا ہے جب اس کے ذریعے مانگا جائے تو عطا کرتا ہے سوال کرتا ہوں تجھ سے تیرے حق کے واسطے سےجو محمد ؐ اور ان کے اہل بیت ؑپر ہے اور ان کے حق کے واسطے سےجو تونے اپنی ذات پر لازم کیا ہے یہ کہ تو محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما نیز یہ کہ تو میری حاجت پوری فرما ابھی اسی وقت اسی گھڑی اے دعا کے سننے والے۔", "RArabic": "AS-ALOKA BISMEKAL MAKHZOONIL MAKNOONIL HAYYIL QAYYOOME WA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA A’ALEMUS SIRRE WA AKHFAA AS-ALOKA BISMEKAL LAZEE EZAA DO-E’ETA BEHI AJABTA WA EZA SO-ILTA BEHI A-A’TAYTA WA AS-ALOKA BE-HAQQEKA A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AHLE BAYTEHI WA BE-HAQQEHIMUL LAZEE AWJABTAHU A’LAA NAFSEKA AN TOSALLEYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWN WA AN TAQZEYA HAAJATIS SAA-A’TAS SAA-A’TA YAA SAAME-A’D DO-A’AA-E.", "ArabicText1": "اَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الْمَخْزُوْنِ الْمَكْنُوْنِ الْحَیِّ الْقَیُّوْمِ وَاَنْتَ اللہُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ عَالِمُ السِّرِّ وَاَخْفٰٓی اَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الَّذِیْ اِذَا دُعِیْتَ بِهٖ اَجَبْتَ وَاِذَا سُئِلْتَ بِهٖ اَعْطَیْتَ وَاَسْئَلُكَ بِحَقِّكَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاَهْلِ بَیْتِهٖ وَبِحَقِّهِمُ الَّذِیْ اَوْجَبْتَهٗ عَلٰی نَفْسِكَ اَنْ تُصَلِّیَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاَنْ تَقْضِیَ حَاجَتِیْ السَّاعَۃَ السَّاعَۃَ یَا سَامِعَ الدُّعَآءِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013643, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my Master! O my Lord! O my Aide! I beseech You by all the Names that You used for Yourself and the Names that You take exclusively for Yourself in the Unseen Knowledge of You to send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and to expedite our relief to this very hour. O He Who changes hearts and sights! O Hearer of prayers!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere sardaar, ay mere maalik, ay mere faryaad-ras sawaal karta hu Tere tamaam naamo ke zariye jin se Tu ne khud ko mosoom kiye (pehchanwaaya), ya usey apne liye khaas kiya ilm’e ghaib mein jo Tere paas hai. Sawaali hu keh Tu Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma aur yeh keh jaldi farma hamari kashaaish (khoosh-haali) mein isi waqt, ay dilo’n aur aankho’n ko palta ne waale, ay dua ke soonne waale.", "Urdu": "اے میرے سردار اے میرے مالک اے میرے فریاد رس سوال کرتا ہوں تیرے تمام ناموں کے ذریعے جن سے تو نے خود کو موسوم کیا یا اسے اپنے لئے خاص کیا علم غیب میں جو تیرے پاس ہے سوالی ہوں کہ تو محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت فرما اور یہ کہ جلدی فرما ہماری گشائش وآسائش میں اسی وقت اے دلوں اور آنکھوں کو پلٹانے والے اے دعا کے سننے والے۔", "RArabic": "YAA SAYYEDAAHO YAA MAWLAAHO YAA GHEYAASAAHO AS-ALOKA BE-KULLES-MIN SAMMAYTA BEHI NAFSAKA AWIS-TAASARTA BEHI FEE I’LMIL GHAYBE I’NDAKA AN TOSALLEYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA AN TO-A’JJELA FARAJANAS SAA-A’TA YAA MOQALLEBAL QOLOOBE WAL-ABSAARE YAA SAMEE-A’D DO-A’AA-E.", "ArabicText1": "یَا سَیِّدَاهُ یَا مَوْلَاهُ یَا غِیَاثَاهُ اَسْئَلُكَ بِكُلِّ اسْمٍ سَمَّیْتَ بِهٖ نَفْسَكَ اَوِ اسْتَاثَرْتَ بِهٖ فِیْ عِلْمِ الْغَیْبِ عِنْدَكَ اَنْ تُصَلِّیَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاَنْ تُعَجِّلَ فَرَجَنَا السَّاعَۃَ یَا مُقَلِّبَ الْقُلُوْبِ وَالْاَبْصَارِ یَا سَمِیْعَ الدُّعَآءِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": 